# workflow.  Commit:                                                          #
#   • package.json, CHANGELOG.md, README.md, LICENSE                          #
#   • Runtime/, Editor/, Tests/, Documentation~, Samples~/… (source assets)   #
#   • .asmdef, .meta (except inside Samples~), images, etc.                   #
